00:08:07,865 --> 00:08:09,698
Tenzo! No!

54
00:08:18,163 --> 00:08:18,897
Yukimi...

55
00:08:19,730 --> 00:08:20,897
{\an1}Are you seriously...

56
00:08:22,196 --> 00:08:23,830
{\an1}...betraying Lord
Orochimaru?!

57
00:08:25,797 --> 00:08:28,163
{\an1}Without the help of
Lord Orochimaru, our

58
00:08:28,196 --> 00:08:29,896
{\an1}clan has no future.

59
00:08:31,963 --> 00:08:33,796
{\an1}<i>That's why Tenzo and</i>
<i>Gotta were willing to</i>

