00:08:35,462 --> 00:08:37,096
{\an1}<i>good of the whole clan.</i>

62
00:08:44,261 --> 00:08:47,762
{\an1}Orochimaru will go to
that village to find her.

63
00:08:48,695 --> 00:08:49,828
I'm sure of it.

64
00:08:50,695 --> 00:08:51,428
Hm?

65
00:08:51,461 --> 00:08:52,294
[gasp]

66
00:08:53,695 --> 00:08:57,028
{\an1}She's gone! Could she have
heard us? And gone back?

67
00:08:57,527 --> 00:08:59,028
To her village?

68
00:08:59,594 --> 00:09:01,193
{\an1}To help Orochimaru?

69
00:09:02,193 --> 00:09:04,327
{\an1}If he gets hold of Yukimi
with her body being as

70
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:06,260
unstable as it
is right now...

71
00:09:09,227 --> 00:09:10,794
{\an1}She's prepared to die.

72
00:09:12,127 --> 00:09:15,459
{\an1}All that I wanted was
to keep her protected.

73
00:09:17,993 --> 00:09:19,459
This time, I...

74
00:09:20,860 --> 00:09:23,660
