you didn't break the rules.

75
00:09:23,693 --> 00:09:24,526
Huh?

76
00:09:25,458 --> 00:09:27,358
Let's go and
protect that girl.

77
00:09:28,892 --> 00:09:29,659
Tenzo.

78
00:09:30,191 --> 00:09:30,892
All right!

79
00:09:48,257 --> 00:09:50,491
{\an1}Where is everybody?

