00:09:51,491 --> 00:09:52,324
[gasp]

81
00:09:58,857 --> 00:09:59,823
[gasp]

82
00:10:06,289 --> 00:10:07,857
{\an1}Perfect timing, Kakashi!

83
00:10:08,822 --> 00:10:11,956
