85
00:10:25,521 --> 00:10:26,955
{\an1}Lord Orochimaru?!

86
00:10:32,388 --> 00:10:33,588
How disgusting!

87
00:10:34,588 --> 00:10:36,954
Inferior things
are useless.

88
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:41,887
{\an1}Well then, it must be
your blood or nothing.

89
00:10:42,220 --> 00:10:43,054
[gasp]

90
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:54,285
[gasp]
E... Everyone?!

91
00:11:00,452 --> 00:11:02,519
This happened
because you were gone.

92
00:11:04,352 --> 00:11:07,451
{\an1}These are the results of my
tests on the Iburi Clan's

93
00:11:07,485 --> 00:11:10,085
