00:11:10,785 --> 00:11:13,218
{\an1}Only with the blood of the
young will this ability

95
00:11:13,251 --> 00:11:14,518
manifest itself.

96
00:11:15,451 --> 00:11:18,818
{\an1}I've already gathered
all the other samples.

97
00:11:18,852 --> 00:11:22,150
{\an1}The only thing that now
remains is your blood.

98
00:11:22,183 --> 00:11:24,584
{\an1}And then that will
be the end of it.

99
00:11:25,051 --> 00:11:28,051
{\an1}But that's... You said
you'd help guide us

100
00:11:28,084 --> 00:11:29,617
{\an1}to the next generation.

101
00:11:31,317 --> 00:11:39,483
{\an1}[painful grunting]

102
00:11:45,182 --> 00:11:46,716
No... No!

103
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:50,315
{\an1}You cannot say no.
I'm going to have your

104
00:11:50,348 --> 00:11:52,515
{\an1}blood, and that's that.

105
00:11:52,949 --> 00:11:53,715
[gasp]

106
00:12:28,913 --> 00:12:32,079
{\an1}[chuckle] Now, do not
waste any more of my time.

107
00:12:36,545 --> 00:12:38,579
{\an1}[gasp] Why can't I?

108
00:12:38,812 --> 00:12:41,579
{\an1}Did you intend to
wrap me up in smoke?

109
00:12:42,013 --> 00:12:43,245
[chuckle]

110
00:12:43,879 --> 00:12:46,244
{\an1}Don't you know by
now the prey can never

111
00:12:46,277 --> 00:12:47,978
{\an1}truly defy the hunter?

112
00:12:48,411 --> 00:12:49,511
[grunt]

113
00:12:51,311 --> 00:12:52,778
[gasp]

114
00:12:53,878 --> 00:12:56,544
[screaming]

115
00:13:00,410 --> 00:13:01,143
Yukimi!

116
00:13:04,343 --> 00:13:05,310
[gasp] Tenzo!

117
00:13:06,310 --> 00:13:09,677
{\an1}Agh! So you've come to
take her back, have you?

118
00:13:10,443 --> 00:13:12,777
Too bad! [grunt]

119
00:13:12,810 --> 00:13:14,242
[screaming]

120
00:13:17,110 --> 00:13:20,010
[evil chuckling]

121
00:13:21,876 --> 00:13:24,076
[screaming]

122
00:13:37,875 --> 00:13:39,441
{\an1}Damn it! Orochimaru!

123
00:13:40,375 --> 00:13:41,042
[gasp]

124
00:13:41,808 --> 00:13:43,407
{\an1}He's losing blood fast.

125
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:45,374
He can't go far
in his condition.

126
00:13:45,841 --> 00:13:47,374
{\an1}He's bound to stop
somewhere in order

127
00:13:47,407 --> 00:13:48,974
{\an1}to take Yukimi's blood.

128
00:13:49,307 --> 00:13:51,173
{\an1}We'll split up and search!

129
00:13:51,207 --> 00:13:53,173
All right! Leave
it to me!

130
00:15:00,569 --> 00:15:01,702
Is that-?

131
00:15:09,301 --> 00:15:11,801
No way... Are
they guiding us?

132
00:15:17,801 --> 00:15:19,334
{\an1}You noticed it, too, huh?

133
00:15:34,967 --> 00:15:35,634
Over there!

134
