[yell]

135
00:15:51,665 --> 00:15:52,798
{\an1}They're on the other side!

136
00:15:56,099 --> 00:15:57,131
Lightning Blade!

137
00:16:20,063 --> 00:16:20,896
Yukimi!

138
00:16:20,930 --> 00:16:22,030
And Orochimaru!

139
00:16:22,596 --> 00:16:23,930
{\an1}You little brats!

140
00:16:25,463 --> 00:16:27,896
How dare you.
How dare you!

141
00:16:29,630 --> 00:16:31,229
{\an1}I won't waver this time...

142
00:16:31,830 --> 00:16:34,428
{\an1}I'll look into your
eyes till the very end,

143
00:16:34,462 --> 00:16:36,261
{\an1}and bring you down!

144
00:16:36,295 --> 00:16:40,762
{\an1}You will only fail. Because
you are still inferior.

145
00:16:40,795 --> 00:16:43,662
{\an1}You will learn your place!

146
00:16:57,194 --> 00:16:57,794
[gasp]

147
00:17:17,826 --> 00:17:22,258
{\an1}I must tell you... You really
need to grow up some more.

148
00:17:22,292 --> 00:17:24,559
