I shall fight you!

149
00:17:26,726 --> 00:17:28,292
{\an1}Stop, Orochimaru!

150
00:17:28,659 --> 00:17:31,157
[groaning]

151
00:17:31,191 --> 00:17:31,958
Yukimi!

152
00:17:33,925 --> 00:17:35,858
Yukimi, no!

153
00:17:37,324 --> 00:17:40,458
[screaming]

154
