{\an1}That's Orochimaru's
Curse Mark!

155
00:17:43,524 --> 00:17:46,091
Kakashi, what
do we do now?!

156
00:17:46,123 --> 00:17:49,857
{\an1}The Curse Mark can only
be released by the caster.

157
