165
00:18:29,587 --> 00:18:30,654
Wood Style!

166
00:18:41,654 --> 00:18:42,753
[growl]

167
00:18:52,453 --> 00:18:53,319
[gasp]

168
00:19:11,551 --> 00:19:12,851
[gasps]

