straight ahead.

176
00:20:43,012 --> 00:20:44,945
{\an1}Into my own future.

177
00:21:04,777 --> 00:21:07,242
{\an1}<i>All I can really do for</i>
<i>now is live by the rules.</i>

178
00:21:08,209 --> 00:21:09,109
<i>But that's okay.</i>

179
00:21:10,610 --> 00:21:12,910
{\an1}<i>Beause now I know</i>
<i>that I'm capable of</i>

