181
00:22:58,903 --> 00:23:00,401
{\an1}<i>It's been a while, Kakashi.</i>

182
00:23:00,435 --> 00:23:03,002
{\an1}<i>He knows how to fight</i>
<i>against my Sharingan. </i>

183
00:23:03,035 --> 00:23:05,702
{\an1}<i>This was his intent</i>
<i>from the very beginning!</i>

184
00:23:05,735 --> 00:23:07,969
{\an1}<i>Why do you want to kill me?</i>

185
00:23:08,002 --> 00:23:09,401
<i>It's my mission.</i>

186
00:23:09,435 --> 00:23:12,501
<i>Stop, Kinoe!</i>
<i>Abandon this mission!</i>

187
00:23:12,535 --> 00:23:15,300
<i>To a shinobi, a</i>
<i>mission is absolute!</i>

